info.description:
## rapidocr-openvino Package

### 1. Install package by pypi. ```shell $ pip install rapidocr-openvino ``` ### 2. Use. ```python import cv2 from rapidocr_openvino import RapidOCR rapid_ocr = RapidOCR() img = cv2.imread('test_images/ch_en_num.jpg') result, elapse_list = rapid_ocr(img) print(result) print(elapse_list) # result: [[dt_boxes], txt, score] # 示例：[[左上, 右上, 右下, 左下], '小明', '0.99'] # elapse_list: [det_elapse, cls_elapse, rec_elapse] # all_elapse = det_elapse + cls_elapse + rec_elapse ```
info.keywords: ocr,text_detection,text_recognition,db,onnxruntime,paddleocr,openvino,rapidocr
